INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES('1684', '490', '_field_3', 'Hello ~\r\n\r\nAre you interested in hosting an evening of Messages from Spirit at your yoga studio?\r\n\r\nI will be visiting Maui in January, 2nd to 9th, and would love to connect with a studio to host this event. I am a psychic medium and have gathered circles across the US to provide messages of clarity, healing, and support for those seeking information and opening to more of their spirit given purpose.\r\n\r\nWhat seems to work best is an evening of parlor messages, in a group setting, and then a day of private sessions. I offer a percentage of the fees to the host studio (on average, 25%), providing a little extra income in times where you may have unused space. The evening session would be $25/person and private readings are $125/hour.\r\n\r\nI would send you flyers, by email that you can print, or by mail, already printed. And just ask that you promote the event to your audience. I am also willing to pay a little more if you would schedule appointments for the events.\r\n\r\nYou can find more information on my website, http://www.enchantedeye.com/messages-from-spirit.html and I am happy to answer any questions you may have.\r\n\r\nThank you in advance for your consideration.\r\n\r\nIn light~\r\nCheryl\r\n\r\n801.577.2248\r\n\r\nhttp://www.enchantedeye.com/\r\n');
