INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES('2082', '551', '_field_3', 'Hello, \r\nMy name is Jessie Wren and I am reaching out to you because I am making a move to Maui in a few weeks and I would be so honored to be apart of your teaching staff. \r\n\r\nI am a 500 hour experienced registered yoga instructor through YogaWorks and have been teaching Yoga for a little over 4 years now. Currently I have been residing in Los Angeles teaching all around the city and I just got back from Maui and there is something about the island that is calling me back. (I&#039;m sure you hear this a lot!) \r\n\r\nIt is funny, I absolutely love Los Angeles and the yoga out here, but there is something about Maui that is calling me to the island that I can not ignore. I am very spiritual and follow my heart, but also I honor the foundation of yoga, and take the postures seriously to prevent injuries. I would love the opportunity to maybe speak with you over the phone should you have any openings on your schedule or sublist. I would be so honored to be apart of your team. \r\n\r\nShould you want more information, I would also love to send my resume. My website is jessiewrenyoga.com\r\n\r\nThank you so much for your time. \r\nJessie \r\n');
