INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES('2156', '562', '_field_3', 'We are so pleased to announce the beginnings of our newest offering here at Sivana!  \r\n\r\nSign up now to stay informed on updates to Sivana Nation, our upcoming yoga /energy healing directory site.  You can view our current pre-launch site at http://www.nation-sivanaspirit.com/\r\n \r\n\r\nOur goal with this new website is to provide our friends and customers with an easier way to access services, information, and everything else that will help them on their spiritual journey.  After all, we are just one big global family!  The new website will include listings of Yoga Instructors, Yoga Studios, Health &amp; Wellness Centers, Reiki Healers, Meditation Teachers, Healing Workshops, Yoga Teacher Trainings, Yoga Retreats, and much more.\r\n\r\nWe hope our current and future friends and customers will use this information to find all the support they need to continue their soul&#039;s journey to greater healing and oneness with self. \r\n \r\n\r\nNot only will this be a great resource for all those truth seekers out there, it will also be a great place to connect to local businesses and individuals in the yoga, holistic health, and wellness communities. Now you will always have someone to share your journey with. We will be constantly updating our listings and site with helpful information, articles, blogs, newsletters, and much more.\r\n\r\nIf you own a business or practice, this is the perfect place to promote it to thousands of new souls. Best of all, the listings will always be completely free, guaranteed! Sivana Nation is just an offering we are lucky enough to share with you and the rest of our global community through the support of our Fashion Brand, http://www.sivanaspirit.com/  (Sivana Spirit).  It is our hope to add a new level of value to our company and to further support all of our customers who support us every single day. \r\n\r\nClick http://www.nation-sivanaspirit.com/ to get registered for your listing before we launch. For any questions, suggestions, feedback or comments, please E-mail us info@sivanaspirit.com\r\n\r\n\r\nThank you so much for your support with this new project.\r\n\r\nWith eternal gratitude,\r\nSivana Spirit');
